    "description": "This is a Virtual Reality (VR) game in which you need to use a Meta Quest Headset and Meta Quest Link software and/or a comparable software. Other VR equipment might work but has not been tested.   You play as a Warlock and endeavor to defeat the evil monsters trying to take over the forest that is inhabited by friendly witches, wizards and creatures but who are hiding in the shadows out of fear of the monsters.  The goal of the game is to defeat as many monsters as you can as the weather deteriorates around you.  With each monster you defeat, you help make the forest a safer place for the friendly witches, wizards and creatures. The more monsters you defeat, the higher your score goes.  Challenge yourself each time to beat your personal best score.",
